column2: ggplot(data = data.frame(mae = c(mae.avg, mae.lpmf, mae.ws), usergrp = as.factor(rep(1:9, 3)), model = rep(c("book-average", "LPMF", "WSLPMF"), each = 9)), aes(x=usergrp, y=mae, color = model, shape = model))+geom_point()+geom_line(aes(x=as.numeric(usergrp), y=mae, color = model, shape = model))+ylab("MAE")+scale_x_discrete("User Groups", labels = c("1"= names(grp_num)[3], "2"= names(grp_num)[4], "3"= names(grp_num)[5], "4"= names(grp_num)[6], "5"= names(grp_num)[7], "6"= names(grp_num)[8], "7"= names(grp_num)[9], "8"= names(grp_num)[10], "9"= names(grp_num)[11]))
